OL,3,CPolitician reveals ADHD diagnosis
OL,4,Cahead of suspension vote
OL,6,FA longstanding Jersey politician has
OL,7,Fspoken publicly for the first time
OL,8,Fabout his ADHD diagnosis, ahead of a
OL,9,Fvote over whether to suspend him from
OL,10,Fthe Assembly.
OL,12,FDeputy Philip Ozouf made a personal
OL,13,Fstatement in the States Chamber,
OL,14,Freferencing when he drove over twice
OL,15,Fthe speed limit in November and also
OL,16,Ffailed to display a valid insurance
OL,17,Fdisc.
