OL,3,CPolitician reveals ADHD diagnosis
OL,4,Cahead of suspension vote
OL,6,FThe proposition will be voted on by
OL,7,Fpoliticians this week and on Monday (8
OL,8,FSeptember), Deputy Ozouf said he
OL,9,Fwishes to "offer a full and unreserved
OL,10,Fapology" for what happened.
OL,12,FHe added: "This experience has been
OL,13,Fprofoundly humbling and distressing. I
OL,14,Fhave felt genuine embarrassment and
OL,15,Fregret for letting down those I serve
OL,16,Fand for falling short of the standards
OL,17,Fexpected of me.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
