OL,3,CPolitician reveals ADHD diagnosis
OL,4,Cahead of suspension vote
OL,6,F"In the last two years, I have faced a
OL,7,Fnumber of personal traumas, including,
OL,8,Fmost importantly, the sudden death of
OL,9,Fmy husband. The effect has been to
OL,10,Fturn my life upside down and to a
OL,11,Fgreat extent, affected my ability to
OL,12,Fsingle-handedly address the volume of
OL,13,Fissues that arise in such
OL,14,Fcircumstances in the ways that I would
OL,15,Fwish.
OL,17,F"I was also advised to seek expert
OL,18,Fprofessional advice for my health. As
OL,19,Fa result, it was established and then
OL,20,Flater confirmed that I was living with
OL,21,FADHD.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
